imdb.plot outline: In their search for Alien encounters, how close is too close? Aliens exist and have visited Earth, and this team is determined to prove it. Operating primarily in the vast open spaces of Eastern Oregon, a small subculture of 'Welcomers' has dedicated themselves to the search for Extraterrestrial activity here on this planet. They compile background data on "hot spots" of Alien-related sightings or phenomena, and then go out with their equipment to see if they can either replicate the reports or explain them scientifically. Their ultimate goal: to find convincing evidence that Alien visitors are truly among us.
imdb.title: The Welcomers
